<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8043131>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27–32. 27–30 head from front: 27. M. myallae Carter (holotype ♀); 28. M. adusta sp. n. (J paratype 12 km N. Paynes Find. BLC); 29. M. adusta sp. n. (J Wurarga, W.A. ANIC); 30. M. adusta sp. n. (J Carnac Island, W.A. SAMA); 31–32 prosternal process: 31. M. incongruens sp. n. (holotype ♀); 32. M. costata Macleay (J Marmor, Q. BLC). Scale bars = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8043131/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8043125>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–18. 13–14 dorsal habitus: 13. M. adusta sp. n. (J Carnac Island, W.A. SAMA); 14. M. adusta sp. n. (J Wurarga, W.A. ANIC); 15–16 pronotum: 15. M. adusta sp. n. (J Carnac Island, W.A. SAMA); 16. M. adusta sp. n. (J paratype Yunta, S.A. BLC); 17–18 head from front: 17. M. incongruens sp. n. (holotype ♀); 18. M. aureoviridis sp. n. (holotype ♁). Scale bars Figs 13–14 = 5.0 mm; Figs 15–18 = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8043125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8043133>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33–39. 33–34 prosternal process: 33. M. adusta sp. n. (J Carnac Island, W.A. SAMA); 34. M. adusta sp. n. (J paratype Alice Springs); 35–39 apical ventrite: 35. M. incongruens sp. n. (holotype ♀); 36. M. costata Macleay (J Marmor, Q. BLC); 37. M. costata Macleay (♀ no locality BLC); 38. M. oculata sp. n. (J paratype Edungalba, Q. BLC); 39. M. oculata sp. n. (♀ no locality, BMNH). Scale bars = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8043133/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

